TY  - JOUR
T1  - Reconceptualizing Stars: Scientist Helpfulness and Peer Performance
AU  - Oettl, Alexander
Y1  - 2012/01/26
PY  - 2012
DA  - 2012/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.1110.1470
